<p style="text-align:left;">
  From there it was down to the totally kick ass city down south, Victoria. Loved the place when I made a short day trip there a few years back so was keen to check it out proper. It feels pretty English to me down there, the style of buildings and I guess even the cool weather to a degree. There wasn&#8217;t heaps to do so I managed to fill out a couple days by just soaking it up and relaxing mainly. Went for a few long walks around the place, good times were had.
</p>

