<p style="text-align:left;">
  So cast your mind back to June when I was in Copenhagen and I saw the replica of the little mermaid. Remember how awesome that thing was? Well Vancouver decided they&#8217;d try and one-up Denmark by positioning a little <strong>woman</strong> in their harbour. I love Vancouver, but this has to be one of it&#8217;s dumber ideas.
</p>

