<p>I’m really happy to not have to live out of a hostel for the 3 weeks before I head to Florida with Mel. The house is about 20-25 mins from the city, and close to UBC (my roomies are UBC students). So yeh, awesome news on that front.</p>

<p>And so that’s where we are up to. I hope you are happy, nameless person ordering me to update my blog.</p>

<p>Yours sarcastically,<br />
Max Power.</p>
